node.text:
The new design collaboration with the world-renowned Belgian design duo Muller Van Severen is now available. Celebrated around the world for their minimal elegance, Muller Van Severen bring their eye for colour and their affinity for simplicity that eschews the ordinary to their creations. For HAY, Muller Van Severen have designed the Arcs Lamp Shades, the Arcs Candleholder, the Arcs Vase, and the Two-Colour Table (the latter dropping in November).

@mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Introducing the New Order Configurator, a professional tool that allows you to envision and design the perfect New Order system to suit your needs! Use the tool to access all of New Order's innumerable components, customize combinations of functional elements, select colours and materials, get prices and item lists, and finally download and save your designs! @stefandiez #HAY #HAYdesign @frame_cph

node.text:
Discover our 2021 furniture, lighting and accessories launches in HAY stores, including our renovated flagship store, HAY House –which is re-opening Thursday 16 September.

1. Arcs Vase, Arcs shade and Two-Colour table by @mullervanseveren
2. Quilton sofa by @doshilevien
3. Knit coat rack by @jinkuramoto
4. Kofi table by @Martin Solem
5. Slant lamp by @branch2018_integrated
6. HAY Play by @claravonzweigbergk 
7. Colour sticks by @scholtenbaijings
8. Phanta plant hanger by @phanta_enterprises
9. Matin wall lamp by @ingasempe
10. Bonbon shade in blue tones by @teget

#HAY #HAYdesign

node.text:
Join us for the inaugural opening of HAY House 2.0 during @3daysofdesign! 

We are thrilled to invite you to our new showroom and renovated flagship store, HAY House 2.0. Come see the latest launches and previews of upcoming collections.

16-18 September
HAY House
Østergade 61, Copenhagen

#HAY #HAYdesign #3daysofdesign

node.text: Designed by Jin Kuramoto, Knit is a simple and iconic coat rack constructed from three metal pipes, creating a unique structure that becomes the feature of the design. @jinkuramoto  #HAY #HAYdesign�

node.text:
Introducing Slant lamp. Designed by Japanese collective BRANCH, it combines bold, graphic lines with a sense of balance –inspired by the power of shapes and how they impact their surroundings.

@branch2018_integrated #HAY #HAYdesign

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HAY on September 09, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text:
Heading back to work or school feels great when you’ve got all the office essentials on your desk. Desk storage, pen holders, notebooks; we’ve got you covered! We’d help make your work environment more productive and beautiful thanks to our range of office products. 
#HAY #HAYdesign

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HAY on September 08, 2021. May be an image of sofa and living room.

node.text: Doshi Levien’s new sofa for HAY, Quilton, comprises generously quilted modules that create a comfortable and versatile foundation for a welcoming living space. @doshilevien #HAY #HAYdesign

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HAY on September 07, 2021. May be an image of furniture, flower and indoor.

node.text: Kofi’s clean lines and timeless quality make it a versatile coffee table that adds elegance to any room. Its flat-pack design in FSC-certified wood makes it an eco-friendly option too. @martinsolem #HAY #HAYdesign

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HAY on September 06, 2021. May be an image of indoor and text that says 'HAY'.

node.text: Sometimes size does matter — in this case: the bigger the better. The new Candy Stripe  XL is spacious and strong enough for storing laundry and other large items or carrying all your gear on outdoor adventures. Made in a strong and durable recycled plastic. #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Formed from a continuous chain of arches that form a single element, the Arcs Shade creates a spatial volume that provides a soft, ambient up and down light. @mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Muller Van Severen’s Arcs Vase comprises a chain of vertical arcs that create an elegant, scalloped silhouette – making it equally beautiful filled with flowers or on its own. @mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Quilton’s extravagantly padded cushions and loungy landscape are perfectly balanced by Kofi’s uncluttered, pared-back design, creating an inviting corner of comfort and contrasts. @doshilevien @martinsolem #HAY #HAYdesign
